{"tid":1503129,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"CECC致信世界銀行 對其給新疆貸款提出質疑","createTime":"2019-08-24T23:33:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T05:38:45.000Z","uid":141151,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7aa7fa00b01574aff15d161bfd558ce2d5cac33e","tid":1503129,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T23:33:03.000Z","msg":"CECC致信世界銀行 對其給新疆貸款提出質疑<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voachinese.com/a/cecc-letter-world-bank-xinjiang-20190824/5054801.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voachinese.com%2Fa%2Fcecc-letter-world-bank-xinjiang-20190824%2F5054801.html&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRUOUDsY8FkShsNjUL6uXjEIs%3D&h=2751d49d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.voachinese.com/a/cecc-letter-world-bank-xinjiang-20190824/5054801.html</a><br />\n<br />\n美國國會及行政當局中國委員會(CECC)星期五(8月23日)致信世界銀行行長大衛‧馬爾帕斯,表達世界銀行對於中國新疆職業教育專案提供貸款的憂慮。<br />\n<br />\n世界銀行董事會在2015年6月批准為中國新疆職業教育項目提供貸款5000萬美元，為新疆近4.9萬青年改善職業技術教育和就業機會。<br />\n<br />\nCECC主席麥戈文眾議員（Rep. Jim McGovern, D-MA）和共同主席魯比奧參議員（Senator Marco Rubio, R-FL)在信中表達了對這比貸款的憂慮，&ldquo;我們的憂慮來源於目前中國政府將超過100萬穆斯林關押在大型的再教育營中&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n信中寫道﹐ &ldquo;我們瞭解世界銀行的貸款是在這些再教育營被公之於眾之前批准的&rdquo;，信中說，&ldquo;我們的擔憂來源於在弄清這些再教育營的性質以及中國政府不斷為其辯護之後，世界銀行仍然在發放這比貸款&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\nCECC要求世界銀行對其貸款資金的用途進行調查，並以書面形式作出回應。<br />\n<br />\n從2014年起，中共在新疆推行維護政治穩定的策略，包括將維吾爾族和其他少數族裔穆斯林關入再教育營。北京辯稱，這些地方是職業培訓中心，目的是培養他們的就業能力。"},{"pid":"28e736e80f3a69bec729e4773194a4e98cda507b","tid":1503129,"uid":36122,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T23:44:13.000Z","msg":"做實事！！<br />\nthis way sir,  this way! <br />\n<br />\n都唔講個&quot;教育營&quot; 實際上係集中營。 就算係真， 你估d錢又真係放晒去個&quot;教育營&quot;咩。"},{"pid":"5be2c1ff05bd058d47a2e0b89d104b137a5cb0df","tid":1503129,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T23:44:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7714940f81ca181c627be9f6710f3f39f4fccbf2","tid":1503129,"uid":188176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T23:45:06.000Z","msg":"開始掘新疆d野出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"103ca58381f4a8b053a40021c77fbbf73dc559a6","tid":1503129,"uid":167938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T23:45:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dd24eec2f017af15a912bbe53e4a41ffb941be0f","tid":1503129,"uid":277186,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T23:46:49.000Z","msg":"Chinazi <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 鬼佬好忌Nazi"},{"pid":"5e2cff8889fcaf64c1680e6666456d4b4e98014f","tid":1503129,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T00:12:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2903fa9b74d88441b4cdfc49b0c25e90b42b19d3","tid":1503129,"uid":7270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T00:13:12.000Z","msg":"【戰術】今日荃灣同往後戰術討論<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1503085\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1503085</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[屌醒勇武] 不進，則退<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1502160\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1502160</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n全民皆兵，打狗救人。<br />\n光復香港，時代革命。"},{"pid":"b8ba733fc60d1f84c8988448a91c695a06abd344","tid":1503129,"uid":7270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T00:13:25.000Z","msg":"【戰術】今日荃灣同往後戰術討論<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1503085\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1503085</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[屌醒勇武] 不進，則退<br 